summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Thirty-second Avenue from a point 300 ft north of East Pike Street to East Denny Way et al in the City of Seattle, by laying watermains under Ordinance No. 21374, creating Local Improvement District No. 2130 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
